{"tid":1224922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同其他人講係立法會上暫緩同撤回既最大分別","createTime":"2019-06-15T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T05:34:57.000Z","uid":22556,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa4448e2747a8e8f35e2e49149ca2b0076418a2","tid":1224922,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"「撤回」不代表永遠不再立法，但程度上比「暫緩」強烈得多。「撤回」草案之後，日後政府假如想重推立法，便要重新走過所有程序，例如刊憲、一讀、二讀等。至於「暫緩」，其實是留有一大條尾巴，日後政府可能隨時恢復二讀，無須再經過刊憲、一讀、二讀等。香港人必須清楚分辯兩者的不同！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8F%90%E6%8F%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6-2003%E5%B9%B4%E6%98%AF-%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6-2003%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E-%25E8%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%2F&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=c1f25977\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6-2003%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E-%25E8%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E6%259A%25AB%25E7%25B7%25A9%2F&h=8f4c829c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%8F%90%E6%8F%90%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6-2003%E5%B9%B4%E6%98%AF-%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E6%9A%AB%E7%B7%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"971a7dd94792a609364af2815d4ce48caa05e64e","tid":1224922,"uid":5813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c07412e4a3d3187c88b937410f0122325a035d1a","tid":1224922,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T05:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不撤不散</strong></span></span>